This product includes a re-implementation of the LG soundbar wire protocol
(custom_components/lg_soundbar_plus/protocol.py) derived from the
google/python-temescal project:

    https://github.com/google/python-temescal
    Copyright 2018 Google LLC
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The protocol constants (AES key/IV and frame layout) originate from that
project. The implementation here has been rewritten (full-frame reads, backoff
reconnect, generic setters) for use in this Home Assistant integration.
